<node id="&quot;ÉTAT-PROVIDENCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"France is a welfare state with unemployment insurance, free healthcare, free education, and social protections."&lt;SEP&gt;"French welfare state that needs rules of finitude to be sustainable."&lt;SEP&gt;"The dizzying growth of the welfare state is everyone's doing, not just the left."&lt;SEP&gt;"The welfare state described as a miracle of immense beauty built by ancestors, to be transmitted unharmed to children."&lt;SEP&gt;"The welfare state grows 4% per year."&lt;SEP&gt;"The welfare state is allegedly collapsing but is actually in full progression."&lt;SEP&gt;"The welfare state is described as potentially collapsing due to debt cancellation."&lt;SEP&gt;"The welfare state is presented as naturally balanced to the French."&lt;SEP&gt;"The welfare state runs ahead because it is doped with the white powder of debt."&lt;SEP&gt;"The welfare state that needs to be saved through sacrifices and an ecology of rights."&lt;SEP&gt;"The welfare state whose survival depends on vital impetus."&lt;SEP&gt;"Welfare state whose ecology would be changed by restoring out-of-pocket payments."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-38bf21a0ee25fcf2d466a7e6e2d4addf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2db9d3bd36cd8348cea1609debc74d1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24d742eda69960bb061851a250ee4933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-554162400a0903cf6577c3382c554e55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-836851f31672854e824bd2729b4feacf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b9c8c579932c3f57dbd96e43240f86b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5b6362abdc9cdd4977a7273692cfc47&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-148534226428b5791469dbc3ec096851&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1818857537526c9ea5ab5cf0b143b192</data>
