<node id="&quot;FRANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"LOCATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"France described as on the path to third-worldization."&lt;SEP&gt;"France finally has a budget after long negotiations."&lt;SEP&gt;"France has insufficient employment rates for both young and older workers."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is a country where global inequalities have not increased at all for 30 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is a country where there is nothing like the death of despair."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is being compared to the US and China regarding technological innovation."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is described as a welfare state country with unemployment insurance, free healthcare, free education, and social protections."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is the country where this political discussion takes place."&lt;SEP&gt;"France needs to become more productive and innovative."&lt;SEP&gt;"France was believed to be fertile with birth rates that would never fall."&lt;SEP&gt;"France was neoliberal in 1958 with Jacques Rueff and became Keynesian."&lt;SEP&gt;"France will strengthen itself industrially and through innovation."&lt;SEP&gt;"France would lose AI if the Zucman tax were implemented."&lt;SEP&gt;"France, a great country with a vocation, the pillar of Europe."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-38bf21a0ee25fcf2d466a7e6e2d4addf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2db9d3bd36cd8348cea1609debc74d1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24d742eda69960bb061851a250ee4933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-554162400a0903cf6577c3382c554e55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b9c8c579932c3f57dbd96e43240f86b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5b6362abdc9cdd4977a7273692cfc47&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0f89f353e6d0ddcbbc4078e20193f7e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-148534226428b5791469dbc3ec096851&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1818857537526c9ea5ab5cf0b143b192&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-520f0299dff0dac110de3f217eb4f3c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aabdbf37bf34f65cdd922b60fe2cedbf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb1a7d5ac51b02dda41de156cbdd863c</data>
</node>
