  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Alain Finkielkraut asks about the Zucman tax proposal."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut asks who installed this cognitive bubble and why it succeeds in political circles."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut is a participant in the discussion who experienced a technical error."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut is a person conducting an interview about social debt and social rights in France."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut is a person questioning the blockage around work culture in France."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut is a person who asks what Nicolas Dufourcq would do if he were in charge, citing Dufourcq's book on the state of French opinion."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut is a person who asks whether the RSA should be touched."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut is a person who concludes the program, thanks the guests, and presents their books."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut is a person who is conducting an interview."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut is a person who moderates the debate and asks questions about RSA."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut is a person who moderates the discussion and quotes Christelle Morencet."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut is the host of the program Réplique."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut is the speaker addressing Nicolas Dufourcq about the ecology of the welfare state."&lt;SEP&gt;"Alain Finkielkraut questions whether AI will put considerable workers into unemployment."</data>
