  <data key="d6">chunk-554162400a0903cf6577c3382c554e55</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Retirement at 65, then 67, deindexation for several years. The generosity of French pensions is now almost absurd.&quot;" target="&quot;RETIREMENT AGE&quot;">
